name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForThyroidDisorders
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Thyroid Disorders
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to disorders that result in a hyperthyroid and/or hypothyroid state and is listed as a chronic metabolic disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes hypothyroidism, hyperthyroidism, thyroditis, thyrotoxicosis and structural abnormalities such as cysts, nodules, and goiters.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes transient neonatal or pregnancy related thyroid disorders and thyroid neoplasms.)
